dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Adam Cox. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Hannah Stewart.
Nice to meet you, Hannah. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is eight seven six five four and my date of birth is zero five two two ninety-eight.
Thank you, Hannah. One last thing, could you confirm your current address and phone number on file with us?
My address is three two one Elm Street, Springfield and my phone number is five five five, six seven eight, nine zero one two.
Thank you for providing the information, Hannah. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Hannah. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
